description: Overall sample: Kaplan-Meier curves for depression onset by parental depression status
Hypothesis 1a: Kaplan-Meier curves for pre-pubertal depression onset (<13) by parental depression
Hypothesis 1b: Kaplan-Meier curves for adolescent/early adulthood depression onset (>=13) by parental depression
Hypothesis 2a: Kaplan-Meier curves for substance abuse onset by prior depression history
Hypothesis 2b: Kaplan-Meier curves for substance abuse onset by parental depression status
